<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>FINAL WARNING: Account Deletion Imminent</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ee0979 0%, #ff6a00 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .urgent-banner {
            background: #dc3545;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }
        @keyframes pulse {
            0% { opacity: 1; }
            50% { opacity: 0.8; }
            100% { opacity: 1; }
        }
        .content {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;
        }
        .critical-box {
            background: #f8d7da;
            border: 2px solid #dc3545;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .timer {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #dc3545;
        }
        .button-urgent {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            background: #28a745;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .button-urgent:hover {
            background: #218838;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="urgent-banner">
        ‚ö†Ô∏è URGENT: ACTION REQUIRED ‚ö†Ô∏è
    </div>
    
    <div class="header">
        <h1>FINAL WARNING</h1>
        <h2>Account Deletion in 24 Hours</h2>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
        
        <div class="critical-box">
            <div class="timer">‚è∞ {{hoursRemaining}} HOURS</div>
            <div>until your account is permanently deleted</div>
        </div>
        
        <p><strong>This is your FINAL reminder.</strong> Your Pathfinder account and all associated data will be permanently deleted tomorrow.</p>
        
        <h3>üö® Last Chance to Cancel</h3>
        <p>If you want to keep your account, you must act now. Once the deletion is processed, your data cannot be recovered after 30 days.</p>
        
        <center>
            <a href="{{cancellationUrl}}" class="button-urgent">
                CANCEL DELETION NOW
            </a>
        </center>
        
        <h3>What happens in 24 hours?</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>‚úó Your account will be permanently deleted</li>
            <li>‚úó All your experiences and career data will be removed</li>
            <li>‚úó Your profile and preferences will be erased</li>
            <li>‚úó You will lose access to all your saved information</li>
            <li>‚úó Recovery will only be possible for 30 days (requires admin assistance)</li>
        </ul>
        
        <div class="critical-box" style="background: #fff3cd; border-color: #ffc107;">
            <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è No Further Reminders</strong><br>
            This is the last email you will receive before your account is deleted.
        </div>
        
        <p>If you did not request this deletion, please cancel it immediately and contact our support team.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated FINAL WARNING from Pathfinder.</p>
        <p><strong>Act now if you want to keep your account.</strong></p>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Pathfinder. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>